      "message": "CPS exceptions, here CpsPathException, are unchecked.\nBut it was decided a while ago that all plural methods in cps should not throw any exception for invalid/non-existing xpath and hence the logging. I don't remember the exact reason because this was a point discussed a few months back. I also confirmed the same with Daniel. Can be discussed further with team. Marking this as resolved for the time being 😊",
